{"step": 57, "message": "{\n  \"chosen_product\": {\n    \"product_url\": \"https://www.rei.com/product/223775/the-north-face-hedgehog-3-mid-waterproof-hiking-boots-mens\",\n    \"product_name\": \"The North Face Hedgehog 3 Mid Waterproof Hiking Boots - Men's\"\n  },\n  \"extracted_attributes\": {\n    \"price\": 160,\n    \"weight_oz\": 32,\n    \"waterproof\": true,\n    \"height_category\": \"mid\",\n    \"rating\": 4.7,\n    \"review_count\": 157\n  },\n  \"cart_added\": {\n    \"size\": \"10.5\",\n    \"quantity\": 1,\n    \"in_stock_at_add\": true\n  },\n  \"reasoning\": \"I filtered/narrowed to men's waterproof mid hiking boots under $250 with size 10.5 availability and sorted by customer rating. The higher-rated Timberland result had only 53 reviews and was excluded by the 100-review soft-preference threshold. The North Face Hedgehog 3 Mid Waterproof Hiking Boots had the highest eligible rating among products with at least 100 reviews, met the waterproof and mid-cut requirements, weighed 2 lb per pair, and size 10.5 was available to add to cart.\"\n}", "terminal": true}
